item.description:
MultiPay allows you to create a single payment transaction with multiple recipients.
Tap to add a recipient (&ldquo;Add&rdquo;) Finish and send the transaction (&ldquo;Send&rdquo;) Add a recipient After tapping the button &ldquo;+&rdquo;
Recipient address or contact name Amount Optional Memo Add the recipient to the list Recipients Address Amount Send After pressing the button &ldquo;Send&rdquo;
Confirm and send the transaction Remarks Multipay does not support using Fiat currency or zats yet Contacts are replaced by their addresses Notes can have an amount equal to 0 Multipay transactions can be empty

You can turn a regular account into a watch-only account. This prevents you or anyone from spending from it. You will still be able to receive coins and monitor the balance.
Making an account watch-only is NOT reversible and you must have a backup of the seed phrase to restore the account later.
Select the Cold Storage option from the app menu Choose &ldquo;DELETE&rdquo;
